title: Don't Allow Critical Voices To Steal Your Dreams | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Don't Allow Critical Voices To Steal Your Dreams | Joel Osteen
description:
Don't waste time trying to prove your critics wrong. When you focus on running your race and pursuing your dreams, God will take care of the rest. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
